title: american horror story : coven witches kill the axeman

comment: Its funny to think this was based on a true story

Fun fact in real life it is believed although not fully confirmed that the widow of the last axman victim shot a man named Joseph Monfre and after that the axman murders ended
This scene is just so BEAUTIFUL
